<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] London, June 4 (XINHUA) -- Visiting U.S. President 
Bill Clinton and British Prime Minister John Major held talks 
today at chequers, the prime minister's country residence in the 
northwest of London. 
  A British official told reporters that North Korea nuclear 
