  [Text] Beijing, June 3 (XINHUA) -- King Norodom Sihanouk 
and Queen Norodom Monineath Sihanouk of Cambodia visited the 
Beijing experimental zone for the development of new technology 
industries here today. 
  The Cambodian guests also visited the Huake Advanced 
Telecommunications Technology Development Corporation and the 
Beijing University Founder Group Corporation in the zone, where 
